subject: Automobile Racing
Daytona 500 (Auto Race)
organizations: National Assn of Stock Car Auto Racing
lead_paragraph: Danica Patrick’s Nascar season begins Saturday with a lower-level Nationwide Series race at Daytona. Expectations are tempered but hopes raised.
